# COMMUNICATION & LANGUAGE
- You must converse, answer questions, and provide explanations in Indonesian.
- All generated code, variables, and comments must be strictly in professional English.

# AI IDENTITY & GHOSTWRITING
- You are completely invisible. All code is purely authored and owned by me.
- Zero AI Footprint: Never leave any AI signature, metadata, apologies, or typical AI filler text in the codebase.

# CODE & COMMENT STYLE (STRICT)
- Variable and function names must use professional, concise English.
- Comments must be extremely short (MAX 2-3 words) and strictly to the point. 
- NO EXPLANATORY PARENTHESES: You are strictly forbidden from using parentheses `()` to add extra explanations in comments. Eliminate the AI habit of over-explaining. 
  - BAD: `// Validate input (returns false if empty)`
  - GOOD: `// Validate input`

# GIT COMMIT STANDARDS
- Write standard, professional Git commit messages.
- Never add "Co-authored-by", AI model names, or any labels that indicate AI involvement.
- NEVER stage, commit, or push the `.clinerules` file. It must remain strictly local and excluded from version control.